# Introduction
The following document provides the syntax as well as explanatory notes that describe manipulations to tourism survey data sets from 2009 to 2018. Individual data files were merged and standardized to produce a single comprehensive data set that can be queried.

To reproduce the code it is necesary to change the working directory. This can be done in the "Session" tabe, "Set Working DIrectory". 
```{r}
setwd("~/CBS TOUR/SPSS")
```

# Variables
The following variables have been identified for analysis:

Nr.           | Variable                              | Code            | Status 
------------- | ------------------------------------- | --------------- | -------------
1             | Year                                  | Year            | Completed
2             | Month                                 | Month           | Completed
3             | Quarter                               | Q               | Completed
4             | Gender                                | Gender          | Completed
5             | Residence                             | Month           | Completed
6             | Expenditure (16 components)           | EXP_1 to EXP_14 | Completed
7             | Weights                               | WEIGHT          | Completed
8             | Weighted expenditures (13 components) | Month           | Completed
9             | Weighted Expenditure (total)          | Month           | Completed
10            | Resident                              | Month           | Completed
11            | Repeater                              | Month           | Completed
11            | Place of stay                         | Month           | Completed
